Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前  被稱作血腥約翰的連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺害了我的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后我們一直在追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自稱為"布萊克組織"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織里還有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  聯調局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一個有秘密需要掩蓋的執法人員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個腐敗警察的秘密組織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰是成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我說了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告訴我殺她的人  也就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底誰是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們很高興地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終于確認了他的身份與面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執法部門負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖局長  就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦法官簽署的令狀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局將立即關閉你們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了  這里沒我們的事兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會放棄  我不信你會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情況我們已經無法掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持聯絡  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切  我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興你能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上塞車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一有空就過來見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況真是一團糟  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽著  我覺得我們...  -一會兒有你說的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們現在肯定都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道接下來會發生什么事  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-探員  -所以我來說明下接下來會發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會找你們每個人談話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單獨談話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有權委托律師或工會代表隨行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你們自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為何需要律師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我們的角度來看看這事  金寶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的上司伯特侖是個罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有可能你們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會非常仔細地審視你們每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們有任何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一點點可疑的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都會發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后起訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  除非
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們能夠配合  那我們會非常非常滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣你們就有點回旋的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(194.4,267.2)}加州  薩克拉門托  富蘭克林區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局展開一場全球緝兇行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通緝著名的薩克拉門托執法部門官員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局方面證實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據信伯特侖就是臭名昭著的連環殺手血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他因在整個加利福尼亞州中心地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯下一系列恐怖兇案而被通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這有公用電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里  你好啊  給我張六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一根菠蘿味雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六合彩  雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用不著捏著嗓子講話  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺真奇怪啊  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們上次...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯特侖  還在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你問的是簡  那我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去樓上找過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也許還沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約一小時前  蓋爾·伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在薩城東區的一個加油站殺了一個警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你聽說了伯特侖當時在加油站做什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在打公用電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜他打給了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是簡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為你清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒法左右你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為你的男朋友和一名危險的逃犯勾結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為他已經深陷布萊克組織中無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是  他也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡無法阻止打給他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他也不是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太遺憾了  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾是個好警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在依舊是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你們在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們聽說了伯特侖今早干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說聯調局的人在找我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在是怎樣  你們就躲在停車場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我們不是躲起來  只是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低調行事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們暫時還安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少現在還沒有下達對我們的逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們遲早會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她剛已經問了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今加調局已經不復存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能靠自己了  你們得保護好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不知道簡在哪里  他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想知道  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明白  頭兒  -明白  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已經不是你們的頭兒了  關鍵就在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(191.4,278.4)}加州  薩克拉門托  威廉蘭德公園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被通緝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說真的  艾伯特給你下了逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你到底要不要告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦對  伯特侖打給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他想說什么  他那時都沒來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么他還在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他會很快再打來告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手機不安全  聯調局...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  他們裝了竊聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們還沒追蹤到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們追蹤到了  我現在就早該被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許如此  但他們早晚會追蹤到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在伯特侖打來之前我不能扔掉手機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以事情就懸在這了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在閃爍其詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鳥的眼睛圓又亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《小恐龍》[系列童書]  你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很清楚他的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -很抱歉我那時不得不掛電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天實在太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  這個電話不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出一百塊換你的手機  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩百塊換你的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什么騙局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百塊  外加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部替代機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥們  我一會兒再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交易愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才到底說了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我們應該見面好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就我們倆  -就像約會一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  游戲結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得說你我確實不分伯仲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然現在一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的覺得我們應該好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停戰  不帶武器  不玩花招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后各行其道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,談談  談什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,談談這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我們都需要有個了結  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在今天  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我時間有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道能否相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到現在了就別膽小了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有那么多機會殺你  卻都沒下手  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  時間  地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小時后弗里蒙特公園的噴泉邊見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不知道那個地方  中央汽車站見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-北入口  -不行  那里人太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且警察太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道亞歷山大公墓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西門那邊有個小教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  半小時之后見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別遲到  我不能待太久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小時之后見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想見我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去見他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我知道自己在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別去  你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局馬上就要抓到伯特侖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想他落在聯調局手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這一天早晚會來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不想讓你牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牽扯  我早就深陷其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要借你的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  你的槍  我不會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是壯壯膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎  請你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,疑犯逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責人呢  艾伯特在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手舉到我能看見的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特在哪兒  我必須得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  淡定點  伙計們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又不是阿爾·卡彭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}著名黑幫老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出來你是個正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以我的名譽發誓  我一小時之后就回去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在  我...  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別別別  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么  你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去見誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回局里說怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  讓她過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  里斯本女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是咱們兩個警察間幫個忙  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  我發誓到時候一定把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底有什么緊急的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是跟伯特侖有約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-加調局  你給我退后  -怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  艾伯特  他什么也沒做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興見到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來不想打擊你們的  但加調局已經不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的警徽就是個玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你們只是在假扮警察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你怎么說  放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是纏上我了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纏上聯調局了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你是真的聯調局探員  有什么證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你們也許是布萊克組織的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出證明來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手下里德·史密斯就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么不可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們怎么知道簡會不會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾伯特探員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在確保他的安全之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護好他是我們的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  放下槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都放下槍  沒必要起沖突
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開我的車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  讓他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了  就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們的槍都放到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照他說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追蹤里斯本探員的車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我車上裝了追蹤器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我們怎么能找到簡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過認識你們這些人我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我知道你們早晚要出簍子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能省我不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這不就照做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還沒準備好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我看會兒車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  會看好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  伙計  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉麻煩你了  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿不愿意載我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里是四隊  我們發現目標車輛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停在第五大道和謝爾曼街交會處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  先退后  他們可能就在那兒接頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四隊  什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四隊  回答  該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  里斯本車里就幾個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發現簡  重復  我們沒發現簡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否收...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再越錯越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是不見棺材不落淚是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  我們真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  你居然還叫他長官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別激動  "頭號公敵"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}約翰.迪林杰是蕭條時期聯調局追捕的最著名的黑幫頭目  曾兩度越獄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在是階下囚  還是識相點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  你以為能弄到個好點的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝[西語]  奧雷利奧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣  祝你好運[西語]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:59.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(78,97.6)}安琪拉·蘿斯金·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:59.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(316.2,99)}夏洛特·安妮·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先得搜搜你身上有沒有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你才能進去  把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試下也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你這么準時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:23:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還真是倆無賴  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證  這是最后一次騙你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先說正事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和聯調局犯了個嚴重的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.34,0:24:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.52,0:24:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.62,0:24:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉讓你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我只是布萊克組織
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.66,0:24:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一員卑微走卒罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.89,0:24:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰可是高層
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.31,0:24:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信是你的權利  但
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.30,0:24:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.06,0:24:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的結論都是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.44,0:25:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么誰是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.31,0:25:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.31,0:25:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.45,0:25:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織嚴格遵循的原則是只須知道必需的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.72,0:25:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假設你說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.19,0:25:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我們完全可以在電話里說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.61,0:25:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我們在電話里說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.27,0:25:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你  你可能就不會來見我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.87,0:25:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.99,0:25:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到命令要打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.93,0:25:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你游戲結束  安排和你見面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.04,0:25:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么要我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.69,0:25:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你千萬不要以為
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.11,0:25:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我樂意這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織不想有遺留問題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.42,0:25:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們討厭留下把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手吧  奧斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:25:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別  別  聽著  聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.79,0:26:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們談談  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.25,0:26:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  這不是我能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.47,0:26:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很喜歡你  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.05,0:26:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別  別  不需要這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.35,0:26:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.85,0:26:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  奧斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以出去等著了  就...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.80,0:26:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確保沒人來打擾我們
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.18,0:26:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.98,0:27:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.46,0:27:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯  你在干
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.01,0:27:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  別這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.75,0:27:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不如周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.51,0:27:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們必須告訴我們到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.14,0:27:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不需要做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.12,0:27:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也什么都做不了  行行好就放松點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.46,0:27:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  我怎么放松得下來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有時候表現的好像你很享受無助感
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.26,0:27:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我收回  別放松
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用額頭把車窗撞破
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.34,0:27:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就可以跳車跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.42,0:27:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙計們  團結一點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.37,0:27:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.94,0:27:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"抱歉"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.97,0:27:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫林斯  你是本地人  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.41,0:27:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  長官  林肯高地的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-給我弄一張薩克拉門托的地圖  -是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.44,0:27:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車里的電腦上就有
